<p><br></p>
<h2 id=3D"expgalaxybeneficiaryv1-POST/beneficiaryList"><span>POST /benefici=
aryList</span></h2>
<p>This endpoint retrieves all <span style=3D"color: rgb(23,43,77);">benefi=
ciaries </span>that the user is entitled to and only return accounts / bene=
ficiaries.</p>
<p><br></p>
<div id=3D"expander-1175536974" class=3D"expand-container">
<div role=3D"heading" aria-level=3D"6" id=3D"expander-control-1175536974" c=
lass=3D"expand-control"><button type=3D"button" id=3D"expand-button-1175536=
974" class=3D"aui-button aui-button-link aui-button-link-icon-text" aria-ex=
panded=3D"true" aria-controls=3D"expander-content-1175536974"><span class=
=3D"expand-icon aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-chevron-down" aria-hid=
den=3D"true"></span><span class=3D"expand-control-text conf-macro-render">D=
etails of retrieving the list of arrangements</span></button>
</div>
