"https://one.dev1.ui.westpac.com.au/npm/docs/ui-framework/1.7.3/core/api-cl=
ient/index.html" rel=3D"nofollow">ApiClient<span>&nbsp;</span></a>helper wi=
ll inject this header parameter.</span></p><p><span style=3D"color: rgb(59,=
65,81);">This will always correspond to the Alfabet id of the main consumin=
g SPA although various micro-frontends and widgets may have separate owners=
hip.</span></p></td>
