<h1 id=3D"expgalaxybeneficiaryv1-Capability:Updatebeneficiary"><span style=
=3D"color: rgb(51,102,255);"><strong>Capability: Update beneficiary&nbsp;</=
strong></span></h1>
<h2 id=3D"expgalaxybeneficiaryv1-PUT/beneficiaryUpdate">PUT /<span data-tea=
ms=3D"true">beneficiaryUpdate</span></h2>
<p>This endpoint updates the detail of the beneficiary.</p>
<p><br></p>
<p><span style=3D"color: rgb(255,0,0);"><u><strong>May 2026 ERM changes ass=
ociated with Confirmation of Payee:</strong></u></span><span style=3D"color=
: rgb(23,43,77);"><span>&nbsp;</span></span><span style=3D"color: rgb(255,0=
,0);">As part of CoP feature, if CoP validation is performed by a maker whe=
n updating a BSB &amp; account no beneficiary, the CoP validation matched s=
tatus Outcome should be included as part of the EXP API request so that the=
 CoP validation outcome can be displayed in the beneficiary details authori=
sation screen. Refer to the SD here for details:</span><span style=3D"color=
: rgb(23,43,77);"><span>&nbsp;</span></span><a href=3D"https://confluence.s=
rv.westpac.com.au/display/ARTC/06+-+SD%3A+Confirmation+of+payee#id-06SD:Con=
firmationofpayee-Sequenceflowdiagram" rel=3D"nofollow">06 - SD: Confirmatio=
n of payee - Sequenceflowdiagram</a></p>
<p><br></p>
