><br></p><p>Non-functional header to provide telemetry and debugging aids w=
hen logged to Splunk. The proposal is to have a single string encoded value=
 with the below attributes to start off with. Other attributes can be added=
 as the need arises</p><p>TYPE: app | browser, PLATFORM: ios | andriod | wi=
ndows | linux | macos, VIEWPORT: xs | sm | md | lg, ORIENTATION: portrait |=
 landscape</p></td>
</tr>
<tr class=3D"">
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
<span style=3D"color: rgb(59,65,81);">x-originatingSystemId</span></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<p><span><span class=3D"emoji-common-main-styles emoji-common-node   emoji-=
common-emoji-image   css-19bdfyn" title=3D":white_check_mark:">:tick:</span=
></span></p>
</div></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
