></span></p>
</div></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
<p><span style=3D"color: rgb(59,65,81);">This header is introduced as part =
of maker-checker to propagate the Channel request identifier (beneficiaryId=
 in this case) to the downstream calls. This header will initially be popul=
ated by the Channels when a maker request is submitted. Entitlements will t=
hen populate this header when calling Exp API after all the checker approva=
ls are received.</span></p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
