<p><span class=3D"status-macro aui-lozenge aui-lozenge-moved">MAY 26</span>=
</p>
<p><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,0);">As part of CoP feature, if CoP valida=
tion is performed by a maker when updating a BSB &amp; account no beneficia=
ry, the CoP validation matched status Outcome should be included as part of=
 the EXP API request so that the CoP validation outcome can be displayed in=
 the beneficiary details authorisation screen</span></p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
