<h1 id=3D"expgalaxybeneficiaryv1-Capability:BSBlooksupforbankname(fieldstob=
econfirmed)"><span style=3D"color: rgb(51,102,255);"><strong>Capability:<sp=
an class=3D"fabric-text-color-mark"> BSB looks up for bank name (fields to =
be confirmed)</span></strong></span></h1>
<p><br></p>
<h2 id=3D"expgalaxybeneficiaryv1-GET/bsbLookup"><span>GET /<span style=3D"c=
olor: rgb(23,43,77);">bsbLookup</span></span></h2>
<p>This endpoint triggers the INF API (<a href=3D"https://mesh.westpac.com.=
au/components/apis/inf-bnkng-chnl-brchntwk-v2?tab=3Dcontract#tag/BranchRefe=
renceData/operation/getBranchReferenceData" class=3D"external-link" rel=3D"=
nofollow">inf-bnkng-chnl-brchntwk-v2 - APIs - Components - Mesh Connect</a>=
) getBranchReferenceData method to <span style=3D"letter-spacing: 0.0px;">r=
eturn bank name based on the BSB provided by the users.&nbsp;</span></p>
<p><span style=3D"letter-spacing: 0.0px;">( The endpoint needs to be uplift=
ed with the bank name in the payload )</span></p>
<p><span class=3D"status-macro aui-lozenge aui-lozenge-moved">AUG 25</span>=
 Due to the DDEP change freeze the bankName uplift won't be available until=
 Oct. For the time being, bankName is to be hardcoded with an agreed value.=
</p>
<p><br></p>
