<tr>
<td class=3D"numberingColumn confluenceTd" style=3D"text-align: left;vertic=
al-align: top;" contenteditable=3D"false" data-mce-resize=3D"false">1</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
Empty response</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
If downstream API returns empty response&nbsp;</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<ul>
<li>Return HTTP status 404 immediately</li>
</ul></td>
</tr>
<tr class=3D"">
<td class=3D"numberingColumn confluenceTd" style=3D"text-align: left;vertic=
al-align: top;" contenteditable=3D"false" data-mce-resize=3D"false">2</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
Input validation</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
Input validation failed</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<ul>
<li>Return HTTP status 400 immediately</li>
</ul></td>
</tr>
<tr class=3D"">
<td class=3D"numberingColumn confluenceTd" style=3D"text-align: left;vertic=
al-align: top;" contenteditable=3D"false" data-mce-resize=3D"false">3</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
Downstream API call error- 400</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
If any of downstream API calls return 400</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<ul>
<li>Map the error details received from downstream to this endpoint error d=
etails</li>
<li>Return HTTP status 400 immediately</li>
</ul></td>
</tr>
<tr class=3D"">
<td class=3D"numberingColumn confluenceTd" style=3D"text-align: left;vertic=
al-align: top;" contenteditable=3D"false" data-mce-resize=3D"false">4</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
Downstream API call error- 404</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
If any of downstream API calls return 404</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<ul>
<li>Map the error details received from downstream to this endpoint error d=
etails</li>
<li>Return HTTP status 404 immediately</li>
</ul></td>
</tr>
<tr class=3D"">
<td class=3D"numberingColumn confluenceTd" style=3D"text-align: left;vertic=
al-align: top;" contenteditable=3D"false" data-mce-resize=3D"false">5</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
Downstream API call error- 5xx &amp; 429 &nbsp; &nbsp;</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
If any of downstream API calls return 5xx or 429</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
Return HTTP status 500 immediately</td>
</tr>
