<h1 id=3D"expgalaxybeneficiaryv1-Capability:Toretrievedivisionsunderanorgan=
isationfortheloggedinuser(Feb2026ERM)"><span style=3D"color: rgb(51,102,255=
);"><strong>Capability:<span class=3D"fabric-text-color-mark"><span>&nbsp;<=
/span>To retrieve divisions under an organisation for the logged in user(Fe=
b 2026 ERM)</span></strong></span></h1>
<h2 id=3D"expgalaxybeneficiaryv1-GET/divisionList"><span>GET /<span style=
=3D"color: rgb(23,43,77);">divisionList</span></span></h2>
<p><span style=3D"color: rgb(23,43,77);">This endpoint retrieves the list o=
f divisions under an organisation for the logged in user</span></p>
<p>Step:</p>
<ol>
<li>The endpoint will query PDP to retrieve the divisions based on OrgCISKe=
y and logged in user's CISKey</li>
</ol>
