rs/{<strong>customerId</strong>}</span>
<ul>
<li><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,0);">name =3D CoP</span></li>
<li><span style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,0);">customerId =3D userId of the logged =
in user</span></li>
</ul></li>
