<h1 id=3D"expgalaxybeneficiaryv1-Capability:ReferenceDataforInternationalBe=
neficiary"><span style=3D"color: rgb(51,102,255);"><strong>Capability: Refe=
rence Data for International Beneficiary</strong></span></h1>
<p><br></p>
<h2 id=3D"expgalaxybeneficiaryv1-GET/referenceData/countryList"><span>GET /=
referenceData/countryList</span></h2>
<p>This API retrieves a list of countries currently supported by W1T for us=
er to select when making international payment or creating international be=
neficiary. It also returns a scenario index for the front end to determine =
which combination of fields to display for a particular country (1=3DIBAN m=
andatory, 2=3DNCC mandatory, 3=3DNCC optional, 4=3DSWIFT/BIC only).</p>
<p><br></p>
