<h2 id=3D"expgalaxybeneficiaryv1-GET/referenceData/currencyList"><span>GET =
/referenceData/currencyList</span></h2>
<p>This API retrieves a list of currencies supported for the selected count=
ry, for user to select when making an international payment or creating an =
international beneficiary. Filtered to only return currencies currently sup=
ported by W1T.</p>
<p><br></p>
