<h2 id=3D"expgalaxybeneficiaryv1-GET/referenceData/bankDetailList"><span>GE=
T /referenceData/bankDetailList</span></h2>
<p>This API retrieves a list of bank details (SWIFT/BIC code, bank name, ba=
nk location, country) matching a partial SWIFT/BIC value inputted by the us=
er. Used during international payment initiation or beneficiary creation to=
 look up bank details by SWIFT/BIC code.</p>
