<h2 id=3D"expgalaxybeneficiaryv1-GET/referenceData/bankDetailListByNCC"><sp=
an>GET /referenceData/bankDetailListByNCC</span></h2>
<p>This API retrieves a list of bank details by NCC (National Clearing Code=
) identifier for a specific country. Searches by partial branch identifier =
(e.g. ABA for US, CNAPS for CN). Used during international payment initiati=
on or beneficiary creation to look up bank details by country-specific clea=
ring code.</p>
<p><br></p>
